"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/777569","Department for Communities and Local Government","false","2017-11-08","<p>The mean prices paid (in £s) for all house types for Cornwall and Devon are shown in the table below for the financial years 2010-11 to 2016-17 (where the years run to the end of March).</p><p> </p><table><tbody><tr><td><p> </p></td><td><p><strong>2010-11</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2011-12</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2012-13</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2013-14</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2014-15</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2015-16</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2016-17</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Cornwall</strong></p></td><td><p>227,594</p></td><td><p>219,055</p></td><td><p>221,614</p></td><td><p>223,804</p></td><td><p>228,585</p></td><td><p>242,553</p></td><td><p>245,222</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Devon</strong></p></td><td><p>239,530</p></td><td><p>230,984</p></td><td><p>235,467</p></td><td><p>237,269</p></td><td><p>252,763</p></td><td><p>260,514</p></td><td><p>268,481</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",,"Lord Bourne of Aberystwyth",,"2017-11-08T16:28:58.14Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/777569/answer","Biography information for Lord Bourne of Aberystwyth","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/777569/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/777569/answer",,,,,"7","Communities and Local Government","Communities and Local Government","2017-10-25","Housing: South West","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty's Government what was the average price of a home in (1) Cornwall, and (2) Devon, in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Lord Taylor of Goss Moor",,"Lord Taylor of Goss Moor","HL2565"
